
  Sirfetchd    Fighting Type Pokémon

  Only Farfetch’d that have survived 
  many battles can attain this 
  evolution.  When this Pokémon’s 
  leek withers, it will retire 
  from combat. 
	Evolution Chain
      Farfetchd ► Sirfetchd

